FBIS4-31074 "dreeu108_a_94002" FBIS-EEU-94-108 Daily Report 6 Jun 1994 ALBANIA Montenegrins Arrested for Smuggling Oil Montenegrins Arrested for Smuggling Oil LD0606082894 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network in Serbo-Croatian 0700 GMT 6 Jun 94 LD0606082894 Zagreb Radio Croatia Network Serbo-Croatian BFN [Text] The Albanian authorities have arrested 25 citizens of the FRY charged with organized smuggling of oil across Skadar Lake. Those arrested belong to a group of Montenegrins from Zeta who were shipping oil to Montenegro. The Albanian authorities arrested them after supervision of cross-border traffic was stepped up in line with UN observers' demands. As of Friday Macedonia [The Former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia -- FYROM] had also stepped up customs control measures, especially concerning fuel.
